data.description: Welcome to this inviting 2-story home, nestled on a spacious corner lot with outstanding curb appeal. As you step onto the covered front porch, you'll immediately feel at home. Prepare to be impressed by the generous square footage this residence offers. The main level is designed for both functionality and style. It features an eat-in kitchen with a convenient breakfast bar, abundant cabinet space, and an oversized butler's pantry that seamlessly flows into the dining room. The living room is bathed in natural light through large windows, and the cozy gas log fireplace in the living room creates the perfect ambiance for relaxation. Additionally, there's a private office at the front of the home.The main level primary suite is a true retreat, boasting a 5-piece bathroom with a soothing jet tub and not one, but two spacious walk-in closets. Vaulted ceilings further enhance the sense of spaciousness and elegance.Moving to the upper level, you'll find three bedrooms and two more full bathrooms, one of which is a Jr. Suite. The basement offers endless possibilities to customize your dream space. It also includes another bedroom and bathroom.Outside, you can unwind on the backyard porch and envision your dream garden in the ample yard space, all while being enclosed by vinyl fencing. Alley access adds convenience to the property.This home is an ideal choice for those seeking both comfort and convenience. Don't miss your chance to make this remarkable property your new home.
